These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, lizard, cat
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Pet   | lizard | rabbit | bird | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
House: colonial, farmhouse, palace, gothic-revival
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
2. the colonial house is on the far left##1
3. the palace house is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| House   | colonial | palace | farmhouse | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, scooter, bus
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport   | scooter | jet-ski | car | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, video-games, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Hobby   | video-games | writing | rock-climbing | woodworking |

