.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, february, december
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Birthday   | december | february | march | september |

